name: 2 Heavies on the Cargo Pad: AN-124 + 747-8F ᴴᴰ
description:
A short video that I shot back in June when the Antonov AN-124 came to Calgary, and was parked right next to a late-arriving Cargolux 747-8. It's not very often that you see 2 heavies on the cargo pad like this. Hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
